+
+/*
+ * mbufs allow to have a gap between the start of the allocated buffer (m_ext if
+ * M_EXT is set, m_dat otherwise) and the in-use data:
+ *
+ *  |--gapsize----->|---m_len------->
+ *  |----------m_size------------------------------>
+ *                  |----M_ROOM-------------------->
+ *                                   |-M_FREEROOM-->
+ *
+ *  ^               ^                               ^
+ *  m_dat/m_ext     m_data                          end of buffer
